data.title: Top 200 Most Common Passwords List
data.meta_description: Explore NordPass' 5th annual 200 most common passwords list. Discover password trends across 35 countries and 8 platform categories.
data.text: For five years, at NordPass we've been mapping out password habits. Sometimes they feel like old tunes that never fade. This year, though, there's an extra layer to the story. We've noticed some patterns, especially on certain platform categories. And with all the chatter about passkeys, one can't help but wonder if there's a better way to do user authentication. Dive into our most common passwords list, see where the trends are heading, and explore the future of passkeys with us.
